{"title":"「2018暑假测评」注意力曲线","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1065#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=1065","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1065/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1065/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/1065"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"榕榕最近报名参加了信息学课。在信息学课上，老师发现榕榕如果一直得不到上机动手实践的机会，他的注意力就会随着上课时间的推移而下降。\r\n\n\r\n\n假设榕榕第一分钟的注意力为 $x$，以后每分钟的注意力就会是之前的 $ \\frac{1}{y}$。如果他的注意力值小于 $100$ 就会严重影响上课效率。\r\n\n\r\n\n现在老师想知道，榕榕在第几分钟的时候他的注意力值会小于等于 $100$，以便老师给他安排上机训练。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"只有一行，包括了两个实数：初始注意力值 $x$，下降速度的分母 $y$。\r\n\n"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出上机训练的时间，单位：分钟。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"### 样例输入1\r\n``` plain\r\n120 1.2\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 样例输出1\r\n``` plain\r\n2\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 样例输入2\r\n``` plain\r\n200 1.05\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 样例输出2\r\n``` plain\r\n16\r\n```\r\n"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$100< x \\leq 1000,1<y \\leq 2$。"}]}